Description: The LWFBrook90R package simulates water fluxes, soil moisture and drought stress using the 
    LWF-Brook90 hydrological model. Different functions provide for convenient simulation set-up and model execution.
    Additional functions allow for parallelization of multiple simulations.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
